{"word":"Rebekah or Rebecca","slug":"rebekah-or-rebecca","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rebekah or Rebecca</b> - daughter of Bethuel, married to Isaac<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=15'>Gen 24:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=20'>Gen 25:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=7'>Gen 26:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=35'>Gen 26:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=6'>Gen 27:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=46'>Gen 27:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=31'>Gen 49:31</a><p/><b>(2)</b> Characteristics of<p/>-- Beautiful<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=16'>Ge 24:16</a><p/>-- Industrious<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=19'>Ge 24:19</a><p/>-- Hospitable<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=25'>Ge 24:25</a><p/>-- A woman of decision<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=57'>Gen 24:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=58'>Gen 24:58</a><p/>-- Modest<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=65'>Ge 24:65</a><p/>-- Brought trouble into the home by teaching her son deception<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=15'>Ge 27:15-17</a>"}]}